\newlabel{fig-icmr_reinf_benchmarks}{{20}{47}{ICMR-Reinf benchmarks (free recall). Simulated serial-position curves (SPC; top left), lag-CRP (top right), and probability of first/next recall (bottom) for mixed vs matched-control lists from Lohnas and Kahana (\citeproc {ref-lohnas2014retrieved}{2014}) under symmetric scoring. Reinforcement at study preserves benchmark fits}{figure.caption.66}{}}
